snippet.title: Kameleon Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Kameleon is a short story thriller and an adventure game from Eight Bit Skyline.

Kameleon is available for free at http://kameleon.eightbitskyline.com

Trailer soundtrack is "The Mooche" by Duke Ellington from Archive.org (Public Domain). Listen here: https://archive.org/details/DukeEllin...
